| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0639 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fba409fa-7273-5e96-8bbf-fe88c560b9bb"
